comments: Okogie (PHX) brushes Monk's (SAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Monk passes the ball.
Ayton (PHX) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Fox's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Ross (PHX) brings his forearm towards Sabonis (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis secures the rebound.
Paul (PHX) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Fox (SAC) is retreating alongside Paul's (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs as Paul spins away from Fox.
Fox (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Paul (PHX).
Paul (PHX) and Fox (SAC) come together at the same spot in pursuit of the loose ball, and marginal contact occurs as Fox secures possession.
Booker's (PHX) right hand comes forward towards Edwards' (SAC) upper body, and marginal contact occurs as Booker's left hand simultaneously deflects the ball away from Edwards.
Fox (SAC) brings his left hand down and initiates contact with Ayton's (PHX) head during the layup attempt.
Craig (PHX) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) firms up on his left leg and absorbs the contact from Edwards (SAC) to his upper body.

Replay review of the foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Booker extends his off-arm out and initiates contact with Sabonis' (SAC) head/face at the end of the drive.
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Edwards' (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) and Edwards (SAC) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Sabonis (SAC) steps forward towards Okogie (PHX) and foot contact occurs as he defends the shot.
Edwards (SAC) veers into Craig (PHX) and delivers contact that affects his pursuit of the rebound.
Booker (PHX) briefly grasps and immediately releases Monk's (SAC) jersey during the inbound.
Craig (PHX) places his hand on Fox's (SAC) side and the contact during the inbound is marginal.
Fox (SAC) establishes himself in Craig's (PHX) path and does not deliver contact.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Sabonis (SAC).
Paul (PHX) brings his hands towards Fox's (SAC) front and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Booker (PHX) briefly grasps and immediately releases Fox's (SAC) jersey during the inbound.
Okogie (PHX) briefly grasps Monk's (SAC) jersey and marginal contact occurs as Monk receives the inbound pass.
Ayton (PHX) and Sabonis (SAC) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Okogie (PHX) brushes Monk's (SAC) arm and the contact is marginal.
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Booker (PHX) gives Sabonis (SAC) a step to avoid the screen and Booker does not deliver contact.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) and Monk (SAC) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Craig (PHX) commits a take foul on Sabonis (SAC). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of the fourth quarter or overtime.
Edwards (SAC) legally contests Okogie's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
